### ============================================
### PRODUCT API - Caffeine Cache Demo
### ============================================

### 1. GET Product by ID (Cache Miss → Cache Hit)
### Lần 1: ~1000ms (query DB), Lần 2: <10ms (cache hit)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. GET Product 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. GET Product 3
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/3
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. GET Products by Category (Electronics)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/Electronics
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. GET Products by Category (Fashion)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/Fashion
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. UPDATE Product 1 (Cache Put)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max Updated",
  "description": "Latest Apple flagship with updates",
  "price": 1199.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

###

### 7. DELETE Product 1 (Cache Evict)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

###

### 8. CLEAR ALL Product Cache
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/cache/clear

###

### ============================================
### USER API - Redis Cache Demo
### ============================================

### 9. GET User by ID (Redis Cache Miss → Cache Hit)
### Lần 1: ~800ms (query DB), Lần 2: <50ms (Redis cache hit)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. GET User 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/2
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. GET User 3
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/3
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. GET User by Username
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/username/john_doe
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. GET User by Username (jane_smith)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/username/jane_smith
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. UPDATE User 1 (Redis Cache Put)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe_updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "fullName": "John Doe - Updated",
  "role": "SUPER_ADMIN"
}

###

### 15. DELETE User 1 (Redis Cache Evict)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

###

### 16. CLEAR ALL User Redis Cache
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/cache/clear

###

### ============================================
### Performance Test - Compare Cache Types
### ============================================

### 17. Test Caffeine Performance (Expected: <10ms after cache)
### Run this multiple times to see cache hit performance
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

###

### 18. Test Redis Performance (Expected: ~20-50ms after cache)
### Run this multiple times to see Redis cache hit performance
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

###
